snippet.title: Atari 2600 - Video Pinball - Game 1
snippet.description: Me playing Video Pinball on the Atari 2600. The game has some serious flaws, not least of all the fact that the ball goes straight through the flipper sometimes, and that I could literally nudge the ball over the rollovers for eternity and rack up a gazillion points, but hey...it's pinball...and I love pinball! This is game 1, which means that the bumper values don't reset between balls.
